      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "GIFYPET * 私の小さなサイバーフレンド Design stolen from A.N. Lucas's Web Lounge! Sir/Mam , Did you dream of your very own pet? Who is there to watch over your site when you are gone? GifyPet will! 😃 This little friend will welcome your guests and love you forever! Best Regards, GifyPet Adoption Center Your site is way k00l with a pet. 1 FPS Render! So no effect to user performance ;3 Belly and Mood System&trade; Customize with your own art! The power of iframe auto updates your pet to new versionz! Slots Minigame $$$ Auto-Friend feeds them when you forget! Design stolen from Lily's Flower Garden! For the custom option, select custom from the dropdown! Use 80x100 images or smaller for pets! Use use a 200x200 image as the map for best results! Keep your art small so it loads fast! E-mail me with feature requests and bugs! Get a Gify Badge for your site! Pet Name: Pet Gender: Male Female Both None Whats your pets element? Fire Water Air Earth Choose Your Pet: Anime Cactus Cat Dog Hamster Melon Flower Frog Ozwomp Robot Custom Custom Image: Choose Your Map: Tree Town Hills Night Sea Forest Ozwomp Custom Custom Image: Background: Gify 1995 Wood Paper Pink Custom Custom Image: Table Colour: White Black Red Green Custom Custom Colour: Text Colour: White Black Red Green Custom Custom Colour: Name: Molly Embed your pet in your website today! Just copy the code below! If you enjoy GifyPet, maybe &copy; 1994-The Universal Singularity - Melo-Phonic Hyper Systems!",
